                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.48g/81: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Crane</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-01-05T16:00:00+08:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 5, 1921—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received January 5—10 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>4. Your 400, December 29, 3 p.m. Conditions of all Legations must be met before
                    surtax can be levied. Entire matter still under consideration. Date [of]
                    beginning of tax not yet certain.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Crane</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
